Fantasy team roster

Source: R/team-roster.R
team_roster.Rd

The players on a team roster with position, injury status, and playing stats.

team_roster(lid, old = FALSE, ...)

Arguments

lid

ESPN League ID.
old

If FALSE (default), return only the current season's data. If TRUE, return a list with all prior years.
...

Additional API query arguments; use "week" as a shorthand for "ScoringPeriodId" to display past rosters, etc.

Value

A tibble (or list) of players on a roster.

Examples

team_roster(lid = 252353)
